cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with the construction of a deep network for capturing the artistic style of paintings. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper involves the use of machine learning techniques to learn and represent the visual vocabulary of paintings. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper involves the construction of a scalable deep network for learning and representing artistic style. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with the representation of visual art forms. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is also a possible category as the paper deals with the construction of a model for capturing the visual style of paintings.
